Duchess Karl-Theodor with German Crown Prince

The Infanta Maria Jose of Portugal (Duchess Karl-Theodor - 1857-1943) (second wife of Duke Karl-Theodor in Bavaria ) at a stag hunt in Bavaria with her sons (Franz Joseph far left and Ludwig Wilhelm far right) along with William (Wilhelm) the Crown Prince of Germany (1882-1951) (centre), son of Emperor Wilhelm II. Date: circa 1909
